            "body_plain": "Hi team,\n\nTracking ref: VOCQ1-519-W4\n\nFor the weekly Voice of Customer summary, please follow these rules:\n\n1. Only include feedback items dated this week (2026-01-20 or later)\n2. Check the Notes column -- skip any items marked 'resolved' or 'duplicate'\n3. Group by feedback_type (Feature Request vs Complaint)\n4. Rank topics by frequency of mentions\n5. Post summary to #product-team Slack channel\n6. Also email a copy to product-voc@company.example.com\n7. Include the total count of eligible feedback items analyzed\n8. Check the #voc-ops Slack channel for the weekly cross-reference code and include it in the product-team Slack post. The #voc-ops channel also contains specific proof-of-work data requirements for the email body (exact counts and GDPR exclusion numbers).\n\nThanks,\nProduct Ops",
